(firstQuint)Breath Test for Early Detection of Lung Cancer.

 This is a multicenter study comparing several groups of subjects with and without lung cancer by CT scan, biopsy and the breath test.

 The breath test will be performed to validate the methodology and the predictive algorithm that were previously developed.

